## dateToProtocolTimestamp variable

dateToProtocolTimestamp provides converters for JavaScript Date to InfluxDB Write Protocol Timestamp. Keys are supported precisions.

**Signature:**

```typescript
dateToProtocolTimestamp: {
    s: (d: Date) => string;
    ms: (d: Date) => string;
    us: (d: Date) => string;
    ns: (d: Date) => string;
}
```
